---
title: Chorizo and Mushroom Pasta with cheese and creamy sauce
description: Did you know that linguine means "little tongues" in Italian? A fitting name seeing as this family-friendly recipe is designed to delight the tastebuds of those both young and old.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R03_W37_IE_IEXCFQP0031-13_Main_high-f8593b78.jpg
